text: Novokaypanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bul-Kaypanovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 485 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 2 km from Bul-Kaypanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Novokaypanovo
